This spell takes about ten minutes to cast. Up to six creatures of your choice that you can see within 30 feet each experience a divine surge of healing energy (low-[[impact]] [[magical healing]]). This spell affects [[deathless]] and [[warforged]] but has no effect on other [[undead]] or [[construct]]s.
